title: Taiyuan Satellite Launch Center monitoring orbit space of Tiangong-1
description: Technicians operate optical monitoring equipments at the Taiyuan Satellite Launch Center in Taiyuan， capital of north China's Shanxi Province， Nov. 8， 2011. The Taiyuan Satellite Launch Center monitored space garbage in the orbit space of the space lab module Tiangong-1 all-day-around with radar facilities in Taiyuan， Luliang， Hancheng and Yulin in Shanxi or Shaanxi provinces. (Xinhua/Liu Bin)
